name: epi_hyperphotogodess
description:
Update: CLIP fix - now we get even more accurate and more beautiful images (Thx to the Explanation about the Model Toolkit Extension by @ndimensional)

I merged it a time ago and don't know anymore which models went into this one (Art&Eros and HassanBlend i can remember), but its my go to Model for almost everything. It was aimed at photorealism but it can do a lot more. Thought maybe it's useful for the public.

U need to use a VAE!!!

I use standard VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned
(added VAE-file for download to the CLIP Fix Version)

For Automatic1111, put the VAE into ...stable-diffusion-webui/models/VAE folder and make sure you set it in the settings.

modelVersions.name: v1 - CLIP fix
modelVersions.description:
Fixed Clip
thx to the explanation by ndimensional in another model on here
